profile:
Handmade custom furniture, specializing in reclaimed and salvaged materials. Offering Harvest tables, live edge countertops, barn doors, mantels and custom installations for your home, office or commercial space. A perfect mix of modern and rustic. 

Bespoke Quality Heirloom Furniture  | Focusing on using traditional wood to wood joinery & historically proven methods such as mortise-and-tenon and solid dovetail construction ensures you will have a piece that will last a lifetime.

Sustainable Eco-Practices | We are dedicated to using sustainable & reclaimed materials in our furniture. Striving for a ‘0’ waste shop through fabrication practices – Reducing the stress on landfills & deforestation.

Giving Back | We are committed to giving back through our Stand For Trees Program.
